---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About & Privacy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 prose prose-blue prose-lg">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight sm:text-5xl mb-8">
      About Sysopoly <span class="text-blue-600">PDF Tools</span>
    </h1>
    
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-10">
      <h3 class="text-blue-800 font-bold mb-2 text-xl mt-0">A Promise of Privacy</h3>
      <p class="text-blue-900 mb-0">
        Your privacy is our priority. <strong>By default, no files ever touch our servers.</strong> 
        Merging, reordering, and deleting happens locally inside your browser. If you opt-in to "Deep Compress", your file is securely transmitted to our backend processor. To ensure zero footprint, our backend operates on an isolated RAM-disk (tmpfs) — your PDF is processed purely in volatile memory and is <strong>instantly obliterated</strong> the millisecond the compression completes. Nothing touches a hard drive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>How is this possible?</h2>
    <p>
      Modern browsers are incredibly powerful. Using WebAssembly (WASM) and advanced JavaScript APIs, we can run complex PDF engines directly in your browser tab for everyday operations.
    </p>

    <h2>Why we built this</h2>
    <p>
      We got tired of searching for online PDF tools only to find they either:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Upload your sensitive, confidential documents to an unknown server.</li>
      <li>Hit you with a sudden paywall right when you try to download the finished file.</li>
      <li>Plaster a massive, ugly watermark across your documents.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This tool is built to be a simple, highly-secure, and completely free alternative.
    </p>

    <h2>Open Source Technologies</h2>
    <p>
      This application is powered by several fantastic open-source projects. We are grateful to the authors who make their work available:
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><strong><a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a> & <a href="https://react.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">React</a></strong> — For the lightning-fast user interface.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="https://github.com/documenso/libpdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@libpdf/core</a></strong> — A modern, typescript-friendly engine for fast PDF modifications.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="https://mozilla.github.io/pdf.js/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PDF.js</a></strong> — Mozilla's foundational library that accurately renders PDF page thumbnails.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="https://www.ghostscript.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ghostscript</a> & Go</strong> — The powerhouse used for remote "Deep Compress" image reduction and optimization.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700">
        Return to the tools
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
